Audio Demo

"Sci-Fi Textures and Loops" are unique sound effects in WAV 24 Bit 96 kHz format that are suitable for creating a dark, mysterious, alien atmosphere.


"Sci-Fi Textures and Loops Vol. 5" includes sound effects such as:


• Sci-Fi Bells

• Sci-Fi Deep Atmosphere

• Sci-Fi Drone

• Sci-Fi Ghost

• Sci-Fi Laser Plasma Movement

• Sci-Fi Lo-Fi Bubble

• Sci-Fi Pulsation

• Sci-Fi Retro Computer

• Sci-Fi Rewind

• Sci-Fi Scary Ghost

• Sci-Fi Texture


Each sound effect of this sample pack has 10 variations of different pitches, loop and non-loop versions.


Product Details:

﻿• 230 WAV files

• 96 kHz/24Bit

• 1.34 GB
